<title>HARK! THE HERALD ANGEL SING</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Ngai un Angelte lasak,
 &quot;Lal thak pieng chuh lopi hen;
 Chamna leng hen, lei chungah,
 Pathien leh gilo chamna!&quot;
 Namtin lawpa kiko in,
 Van mite la sakpih un;
 Angelte gensa bang khan,
 &quot;Krista pieng Bethelhem ah.&quot;
 Ngaiun Angelte lasak,
 &quot;Lal thak pieng chuh lopi hen.&quot;

[V2]
 2. Van mite chawihat Krista,
 Kumsawt Lalpa Krista chu;
 Sawttak nungin A hung pieng,
 Nungak thiengtho sung a pat.
 Pathien, mihiem mel hun pun,
 Chawian un, Pathien mihiem;
 Mihiem laka chen a nuom,
 Lal Isu Immanuel.
 Ngaiun Angelte lasak,
 &quot;Lal thak pieng chuh lopi hen.&quot;

[V3]
 3. Van chamna Lal chawian un,
 Felna Nisa chawian un;
 Vak leh hinna A hun tun,
 A tha nuoiah damna um.
 A lopina hun kawihthan,
 Kumsawt hinna din A pieng;
 Leimi hinkit nan A pieng.
 I pienthakna din A pieng,
 Ngaiun Angelte lasak,
 &quot;Lal thak pieng chu lopi hen.&quot;</lyrics>
</song>